{"tid":841961,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"原來飼養兔仔可令人心境平靜！🌟","createTime":"2018-09-30T02:16:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-30T14:40:15.000Z","uid":197098,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"ffd84776e6ca9c20e84b47afc32c95b62422e1b0","tid":841961,"uid":197098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T02:16:50.000Z","msg":"兔子是其中一種最心境平靜的動物，很多人覺得牠們尤其是咀嚼食物的聲音很治癒。如果你家的兔子有攻擊性，這不是兔子的本性，而是後天環境和飼養方式影響的。兔子亦被作為情緒和心靈支持動物(emotional support animal)，即是主人有醫生的證明，帶着小動物作伴，心靈才得到慰藉。<br />\n<br />\n以下video可看到兔子拚命地拯救一隻被困住的貓! 真感人！☺<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ydwwZtQyuiU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FydwwZtQyuiU&d=CMZvBETLpSXbKaXFH7%2BYub%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=80cd13b9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ydwwZtQyuiU</a><br />\n<br />\n當兔子跳兔子舞(Binky)時, 這是告訴你是一個好主人，代表牠很喜歡現時的環境和生活，因為兔子Binky是兔子最開心的狀態。以下video可看到：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pqOeRBSpaCs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpqOeRBSpaCs&d=CMZvBETLpSXbKaXFH7%2BYub%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=db54af17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pqOeRBSpaCs</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">N.B.: </span>實在有太多主人遺棄兔子，主要原因是不理解兔子,覺得牠們悶不親近人。兔子是聰明、群體性動物。如果想養，可在兔友協會<span style=\"color: green;\"><strong>參觀然後領養</strong></span>，這裏有太多兔子需要一個家。詳情可去 <a href=\"http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkrabbit.org%2F%3Fpage_id%3D114&d=CMZvBETLpSXbKaXFH7%2BYub%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=24a38d0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkrabbit.org/?page_id=114</a>"},{"pid":"47852e5c13eb0e90420160e33a099c0ffcb573a3","tid":841961,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T04:24:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0j8Gt5JQPKc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0j8Gt5JQPKc&d=CMZvBETLpSXbKaXFH7%2BYub%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=7e4f5725\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0j8Gt5JQPKc</a>"},{"pid":"ce6ae71b3bd264f4f050b021cd37c1afde834735","tid":841961,"uid":69899,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T04:36:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb3e8783e79e9780c265e580f41368380e09c6c7","tid":841961,"uid":204157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T05:50:30.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c5f1ef3b6253edc401ebcf15dfc82ac452b8684","tid":841961,"uid":53105,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T06:14:28.000Z","msg":"紅燒"},{"pid":"3ae725fc029e3c40e566cee1f9c88836b26ceb45","tid":841961,"uid":35468,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T06:15:42.000Z","msg":"可以玩又可以食 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8ecf2e52ac4ae738f1ddebeb8c942e78ff46c3a","tid":841961,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T10:57:38.000Z","msg":"......"},{"pid":"ea675d3f134fe1bf6b3795ec239919956d5da17f","tid":841961,"uid":59221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T11:28:30.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有養兔仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"935d9eb7f20ead1f1366c84ff9ac14bfc53bb628","tid":841961,"uid":197098,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ea675d3f134fe1bf6b3795ec239919956d5da17f","tid":841961,"uid":59221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-30T11:28:30.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有養兔仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"repl